      *
     C                     END
     C                     END
     C  N10                END
      *
     OABEWP06 EADD             GDT
     O                         $KCD1      1
     O                         $ZOGN      2
     O                         $TKRO      8
     O                         $SHIN     20
     O                         $KSTS     29
     O                         $ZSTS     38
     O                         $ZGSU     47
     O                         $N1SU     56
